From a488d9fb2019bb831ccd86707bf482f9a2bc0dd6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Thu, 25 Jun 2026 12:56:45 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix builder wizard: sticky header, icons, risks block,
 layout, badge text, PDF export
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Remove overflow-x: hidden from .main to fix position: sticky on PageHeader
- Replace text arrows with Lucide ArrowLeft/ArrowRight icons on all wizard nav buttons
- Remove "Базовый объём" badge from StepArtifacts card
- Merge RISK_GROUPS into single block with sub-group labels (matching v1)
- Fix badge/statsLeft text: "баллов" instead of "ЭБ" on steps 3-4
- Move size (SM/MD/LG) to left side of ebCard in StepResult
- Fix total row in StepResult: "баллов" instead of "ЭБ"
- Add PDF export button (window.print) to StepResult footer
- Fix ProgressSteps isDone logic: n !== current && n <= maxReached

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_015VS695STjsRgYbcZEUab6A
